<p style="margin:8px 0 0;color:#5b6473;font-size:14px">A 16-session arc moving from <b>understanding culture</b> → <b>diagnosing change</b> → <b>resistance &amp; systemic change</b> → <b>executing change</b> → <b>leading change</b>.</p>
